            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1619781724233-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>brioche buns</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 3-4 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Once done, set aside until serving</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
